  "caption": "Figure 4. .Alphaflexiviridae. Unrooted phylogenetic (distance) tree based on the amino acid sequences of the capsid protein of members of the family Alphaflexiviridae . Virus genera are indicated to the right of their respective branches. Numbers on branches indicate percentage of bootstrap support out of 1000 bootstrap replications (when >70%). The scale indicates JTT amino acid distances. Tree produced in MEGA7 ( Kumar et al., 2016 ). This phylogenetic tree and corresponding sequence alignment are available to download from the Resources page .",
